Vegan Carrot soup
https://www.thespruceeats.com/creamy-vegan-carrot-soup-with-coconut-3377977

Ingredients
2 to 3 large carrots (chopped small)
1 onion (chopped small)
1 teaspoon fresh ginger (minced)
1 1/2 teaspoon curry powder
1 3/4 cup vegetable broth <-- Maggi, code 12345.
1 (14-ounce) can coconut milk
Salt (to taste)


Step 1:
Set up stove in medium heat (6/10)
Add the carrots, onions, ginger, and curry powder to a soup pot and cover with the vegetable broth. Simmer for 20 minutes, until carrots are soft.

Step 2:

Allow to cool slightly (for 3 min), and then puree in a blender, working in batches if needed.

Step 3:
Return to the heat and stir in coconut milk until well combined.

Step 4:
Season generously with sea salt, to taste.


